name: HS - Freddie Mercury #87
description: Introducing the original NFT photography in honor of the amazing era of Rock and Roll by Swiss Photography Hannes Schmid. The artbox collection includes five photographs, united under the series of ‘Blackstage' which consists of a selection of the most famous Rockstars, in a unique composition of the stage light and the performer with the additional attribute of Hannes talking about his relationship to these Rockstars.
